title: A Cid Symphony - A Cid Symphony (1968/1999) [FLAC]
description:
A Cid Symphony - A Cid Symphony (1968/1999)

Genre: US, Acid Folk

2-CD set is an ultra-rare 1967 album that originally was released as a triple-LP; the group contains the leaders of the Berkeley Free Speech Movement - it traces their performance at the Monterey Pop Festival & the Golden Gate Human Be-ins, to their Fantasy studio sessions from 1966-67 - it's trippy psychedelic folk/blues
